{"tid":1464142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實818大遊行終點站係機場有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:29:18.000Z","uid":207418,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0d2b7ea9dd637658492ea1bcf9baa7026ced7969","tid":1464142,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:29:39.000Z","msg":"鑑於小妹尋日去機場誤信未FC嘅信息同fd一齊走咗，仲因為等唔到巴士又逼唔到機鐵所以就跟大隊行路出東涌站，on99咁行咗大概一個鐘，沿途風景都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且，會令車輛行駛更<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不暢順</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋終點喺機場嘅話，可以順便<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和你飛</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家又可以喺機場涼下冷氣食下嘢休息下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一嚟大家可以搭巴士或狗鐵去東涌，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">唔洗搭去機場咁貴</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學生哥可以慳翻少少，二嚟可以比各位義士<span style=\"font-size: large;\">行完休息下</span>，三嚟<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔驚班狗武力清場</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />四嚟可以繼續<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">百萬人癱瘓機場</span>，鏈撚爆中共春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過如果真係實行嘅話大家最好帶多一件黑衫去到機場換（費事臭死自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），同埋例牌帶多一件衫喺機場走嗰陣換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：有得諗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咪撚on9啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎表達意見，<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有錯屌細力啲</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzhLvb3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzhLvb3.png&h=d685f3c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋日個天真係好靚，不過最靚嘅係香港人"},{"pid":"73c15b334dd1050194048f340dbb8c6e97e72659","tid":1464142,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:30:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a26952c721a29f426a0ed53cf6c8c9d8c7cc3606","tid":1464142,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:30:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cd592d7d553d5996970097e154397d1fcf2a78b2","tid":1464142,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:30:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0c5cd587f620502c3a2acf037f04444cc6e4d978","tid":1464142,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:31:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0456617848c4bad54bc751c9de17136a254bf61d","tid":1464142,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:31:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e29109edc40dab2b61238bd32c1f2bd3131d27c0","tid":1464142,"uid":68471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"4c67388b891629d2db8e52228eb5f83e441bb660","tid":1464142,"uid":207418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:31:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"acfc2862e4